"1 pound ground chicken, preferably a mixture of 1/2 white and 1/2 dark meat","1/2 cup shredded sharp cheddar cheese","1/3 cup grated parmesan cheese","1 teaspoon minced garlic","1/2 teaspoon kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1/3 cup mayonnaise","1/4 cup finely chopped fresh basil","1 tablespoon each fresh lemon juice and finely shredded lemon zest","4  onion kaiser rolls, split","8  strips bacon (about 8 oz.), cooked until crisp","1  large tomato, thinly sliced","4  leaves romaine lettuce"